name: HabitTracker
0:
”Alexa, tell Habit Tracker did it”
”Alexa, ask Habit Tracker what's my high score”
”Alexa, ask Habit Tracker what's my streak”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: habit tracker
des: Habit tracker lets you easily keep track of a habit. To update a habit everyday, just say Did It. You can invert between positive habits (built up everyday, say Did It everyday) and negative habits (built up automatically and broken when you do something, say Did It to break streak) by using the Invert command.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
